# Data handling
- No PII logging. Provide a redaction utility for logs and reports.
- Support full offline mode; telemetry disabled by default.

# Packaging
- Provide Dockerfiles with non-root user, pinned deps, and reproducible builds.
- Supply SBOM for enterprise builds (e.g., pip-audit / syft).
